function Client_PresentSettingsUI(root)
	UI.CreateLabel(root).SetText("When an attack is made, surviving attackers immediately continually attack the same defending territory on the same turn until either (A) target territory is captured, (B) all attackers die, (C) neither attackers or defenders take damage anymore or (D) up to a max of 100 repeated attacks. Read Mod description for more details and sample figures.\n");
end